<ul>
<li>1.首先找到python3.6的安装目录C:\Program Files\Python36，右键单击python36文件夹</li>
<li>2.按下面截图操作：<br><img src="http://i.imgur.com/BsyfWLX.png" alt=""><br><img src="http://i.imgur.com/t3e8AX4.png" alt=""><br>最后在Users的权限-&gt;完全控制-&gt;允许：打勾即可</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="pycharm汉化版"><a href="#pycharm汉化版" class="headerlink" title="pycharm汉化版"></a>pycharm汉化版</h2><ul>
<li>1.下载<a href="&#39;https://github.com/adminlinzi/mygitworks/blob/master/resources_zhCN.jar&#39;">resources_zhCN.jar</a></li>
<li>2.将文件放进安装目录的/lib/里，我的是C:\Program Files (x86)\JetBrains\PyCharm 2016.3.1\lib</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
    
